Mr. Gates...

05:42.274 --> 05:46.104
we appreciate everything you've
done, we're grateful. - You're grateful?

05:46.139 --> 05:48.808
But we've changed.
- Changed?

05:48.914 --> 05:52.852
You want out. Think about
the things that we've seen

05:52.852 --> 05:54.937
and we've done together.

05:56.088 --> 05:59.531
Oh, no. There's no getting out.

05:59.892 --> 06:02.306
Let me tell a story.

06:03.596 --> 06:05.687
When I was a kid
growing up in Scotland,

06:06.298 --> 06:09.826
my old man used
to breed chickens.

06:10.603 --> 06:13.962
One night when he
was on his usual bender,

06:14.039 --> 06:17.114
I heard this noise
coming from the hen house.

06:17.476 --> 06:20.899
And it was this red
fox standing there

06:21.180 --> 06:23.743
with a hen in his mouth.

06:25.017 --> 06:29.732
So I raised up my end field
and I had him in my sights.

06:32.258 --> 06:34.118
Aye, he was there.

06:36.629 --> 06:39.645
I couldn't pull the trigger.

06:40.165 --> 06:41.771
Couldn't do it.

06:43.002 --> 06:45.671
So the next day...

06:45.671 --> 06:51.501
daddy dear, is standing waiting
for me... with a leather strap.

06:53.679 --> 06:56.576
And he beat me with
that thing for an hour.

06:58.284 --> 07:02.484
So later that night,
when the fox came back

07:03.956 --> 07:07.144
I opened up the coop
and I let him in.

07:08.160 --> 07:12.593
And he killed every
one of them chickens.

07:12.965 --> 07:16.851
And that was the last
fox I ever let away.

07:17.670 --> 07:19.902
Mr. Gates please.

07:20.172 --> 07:22.361
We just want
a clean slate, okay?

07:22.474 --> 07:24.722
I did what you
asked us to do.

07:26.512 --> 07:27.801
