07:51.303 --> 07:53.217
Sleep tight, you two.

07:56.175 --> 07:59.659
You're wondering why
you're still alive, aren't ya?

08:00.079 --> 08:05.181
I got one more job for you.
- Never! - Oh, I think you will. - Dad?

08:05.317 --> 08:07.652
Stop, son stop!
- Whoa, little leak.

08:13.258 --> 08:17.763
You do this job for me,
you and the boy get to live.

08:17.763 --> 08:22.569
My boy has nothing to do
with this. - Well, that's a shame.

08:22.604 --> 08:26.160
Then the boy has to die
for the sins of his father.

08:27.740 --> 08:30.689
Shoot him.
- No, no! Stop, don't!

08:32.778 --> 08:35.120
I'll do it.
- Dad!

08:36.615 --> 08:39.049
Of course you will.

08:40.119 --> 08:41.520
Good boy.

08:47.899 --> 08:50.513
LEGAL ACTION

