charges of shoplifting against your client,

09:32.738 --> 09:34.607
not some drummed up civil case.

09:34.642 --> 09:36.567
You and I are just
having a friendly discourse,

09:36.575 --> 09:38.062
Before we pass
the point of no return.

09:38.063 --> 09:40.702
