16:38.997 --> 16:40.912
I got Jonah and the whale.

16:43.902 --> 16:46.464
Crime and punishment.

16:47.572 --> 16:49.887
Crime and punishment, brother.

16:56.715 --> 16:58.991
Hey, you tell Gates I did
everything he asked, alright?

16:59.551 --> 17:01.456
I did everything that he asked.

17:01.953 --> 17:04.223
Well then, you just
keep on playing the game.

17:04.789 --> 17:07.105
Yeah, that ain't part of the deal.
- 'Cause you got caught.

17:10.929 --> 17:12.098
Now...

17:13.231 --> 17:15.724
you don't talk
to no lawyers.

17:16.034 --> 17:17.828
Don't titter-tatter to your sister.

17:19.204 --> 17:21.167
You know we'll
know if you do.

17:23.097 --> 17:24.240
If you do...

17:25.577 --> 17:26.573
well...

17:27.656 --> 17:29.615
you know what
I'm gonna have to do.

17:31.816 --> 17:34.786
Where's Kit?
Where's my boy?

17:34.786 --> 17:37.448
Where is my boy?
- Oof!

17:42.561 --> 17:43.600
Safe.

17:44.796 --> 17:46.517
Just like a little
bird in the hand.

17:47.599 --> 17:51.339
If you lay one hand on my boy,
okay... one hand and I will rip your...

17:51.374 --> 17:53.680
Oh, you're gonna rip my?
