17:55.106 --> 17:56.519
Go on a hunger strike?

17:58.176 --> 18:01.270
You gonna write the lawyers?
Gonna speak to the governor?

18:05.617 --> 18:09.614
You know, we know that you got
an outside pinch-hitter coming in...

18:10.355 --> 18:11.521
Your brother in law.

18:12.057 --> 18:14.096
I've always hated lawyers.

18:14.659 --> 18:17.360
Please, please just

18:17.862 --> 18:19.703
give me a half
a reason to hurt him.

18:28.707 --> 18:30.642
Sleep sweet.

18:34.946 --> 18:37.682
Hey! - Books, bibles,
magazines. - Hey!

18:40.218 --> 18:43.369
Books, bibles, magazines.

18:44.956 --> 18:47.280
Books, bibles, magazines.

20:17.415 --> 20:21.123
You look lost.
- No, just calibrating.

20:21.319 --> 20:23.555
Looking for the courtroom
where they're holding Chambers case.

20:23.852 --> 20:26.554
Ben Wingwright, just
sworn in as special prosecutor.

20:26.858 --> 20:29.049
