20:36.267 --> 20:39.370
They brought in judge
Thorne from two counties over

20:39.370 --> 20:41.959
For the case, too.
Good luck with that.

20:43.241 --> 20:44.905
Courtroom's upstairs.

20:49.214 --> 20:51.277
I've always loved
this courtroom;

20:51.312 --> 20:53.590
It's a thing of beauty.

20:54.753 --> 20:56.862
The windows are
the original panes,

20:56.897 --> 20:58.829
the seats were refurbished

20:59.057 --> 21:02.237
From the original bleachers
of fenway park. Go figure.

21:09.768 --> 21:11.635
I'm glad to have run
into you, mr. Wingwright.

21:11.836 --> 21:13.683
Please, Ben's easier.
- Ben.

21:13.972 --> 21:17.043
I was thinking that before iI met
with my client here... - He's kin, isn't he?

21:18.877 --> 21:22.378
He is, by association. He just
sorta came with the ex-wife.

21:22.814 --> 21:24.321
So it's a favor to her.

21:24.349 --> 21:26.568
I was hoping to test
the waters on a plea deal.

21:28.264 --> 21:29.978
25?
