21:31.322 --> 21:34.273
40? Be out in 20.

21:34.959 --> 21:36.089
Hm.

21:36.928 --> 21:39.616
How about plea
guilty to trespassing and

21:39.798 --> 21:43.170
carrying an illegal firearm?
